3. Retro Source

The Retro Source is a modified, limited version of the Game that is made available for modding and creating games using the RetroFutureGameEngine. By accessing and using Retro Source, you agree to the following conditions:

Retro Source is provided for the purpose of creating custom mods, content, and games based on the Retro Future universe.
You may modify, distribute, and use Retro Source solely for personal, non-commercial purposes or within the guidelines of the RetroFutureGameEngine.
You may not sell or monetize any modifications or derivative works made from Retro Source without explicit permission from the developer.
The developer retains all ownership rights to the original Retro Source and any content within it.
